The,posps,web,service,defines,an,interface,between,a,point,of,sale,POS,and,a,pharmacy,s,IT,system,PS,Posps,goal,is,to,reuse,the,business,logic,and,data,storage,that,exist,in,the,pharmacy,s,IT,systems,for,new,points,of,sale,This,allows,a,POS,that,s,been,newly,integrated,by,the,pharmacy,to,present,the,full,functionality,and,knowledge,of,the,PS,without,the,need,to,redundantly,store,and,update,data,across,systems,The,posps,interface,can,be,programmatically,integrated,with,pharmaceutical,systems,using,its,SOAP,based,API